# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.3.0] - Unreleased



## [0.2.0] - 2025-05-14

### Added

- improve documentation
- add support for CSS '--antialias-diff-color and --diff-color custom properties
- react to CSS custom property changes

### Fixed

- Fix main file not defined in package.json
- Fix inconsistent image size


## [0.1.0] - 2024-09-10

### Added

- First release, the component is usable. Needs more testing and documentation


